  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">COMMIT Command</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><snippet src="__CommandInclude" inline="false"/></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Heading1">Purpose</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">Flush all pending updates in all work areas.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Heading1">Syntax</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">COMMIT [ALL]</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Heading1">Description</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">COMMIT causes all pending updates to all work areas to be written to disk. &#160;It is functionally equivalent to DBCommit() for every occupied work area. &#160;<br/>COMMIT <text style="font-weight:bold;">ALL</text> is functionally equivalent to DBCommitAll().</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">All updated database and order buffers are written to disk, and a OS Commit request is issued for all files associated with all work areas.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Heading1">Notes</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="BoldItalic" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;">Shared mode: &#160;</text>COMMIT makes database updates visible to other processes. &#160;To insure data integrity, issue DBCommit() before an unlock operation. &#160;</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Heading1">Examples</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">In this example, COMMIT forces a write to disk after a series of memory variables are assigned to field variables:</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; color:#ff0000;">USE</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; color:#000000;"> sales </text><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; color:#ff0000;">EXCLUSIVE</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; color:#000000;">&#32;</text><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; color:#ff0000;">NEW</text><br/><br/><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; color:#ff0000;">APPEND</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; color:#000000;">&#32;</text><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; color:#ff0000;">BLANK</text><br/><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; color:#ff0000;">REPLACE</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; color:#000000;"> Sales-&gt;Name </text><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; color:#ff0000;">WITH</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; color:#000000;"> &quot;Jones&quot;</text><br/><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; color:#ff0000;">REPLACE</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; color:#000000;"> Sales-&gt;Amount </text><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; color:#ff0000;">WITH</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; color:#000000;"> 123.45</text><br/><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; color:#ff0000;">COMMIT</text></para>
